  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<E>, Collection<E>, List<E>, javafx.beans.Observable, javafx.collections.ObservableList<E>

    public class ObservableListRef<E>
extends RefList<E>
implements javafx.collections.ObservableList<E>
    A JavaFX ObservableList backed by a Ankor Ref that references a List. The list items of this observable list are directly retrieved from the underlying "collection" Ref. Listeners of this observable get notified whenever the referenced list's content changes.
    Author:
    Manfred Geiler
